items.title: Trump admin live updates: Trump calls for special prosecutor for 2020 election
items.description: Trump took to Truth Social Friday morning to again make unverified claims that the 2020 election was fraudulent and called for a special prosecutor.

items.title: Mahmoud Khalil ordered released by federal judge
items.description: A federal judge has ordered the release of Columbia University pro-Palestinian activist Mahmoud Khalil.

items.title: WATCH:  ‘I’m pretty lucky’: Teen struck by lightning as thunderstorms hit Northeast
items.description: In New York City, a teenager was struck by lightning in Central Park Thursday afternoon, police said. The boy is alert and conscious, police said.

items.title: Israel-Iran live updates: Iranian FM open to continue discussions after Geneva talks
items.description: UK, France and Germany said there were no major breakthroughs on Friday.
